Rollplay Nighthawk Bolt 12 Volt Ride On Toy for Ages 4 & Up with Compact Design for Easy Storage, Side Handlebars for Steering, and a Top Forward Speed...

Compact and lightweight ride-on toy is packed with fun-filled excitement for outdoor entertainment; Designed perfectly for riders 4 years of age and older
Boasts a forward speed of up to 4 miles per hour with fun, fast steering, just lean left and right to carve a turn; Contoured seat provides rider with comfortable seating and maximum support
Side safety handlebars help the rider master the art of maneuvering; Accessible foot pedal for easy acceleration; Tail flag helps you easily spot your child
Compact design allows you to take the vehicle virtually anywhere and store when done so it would be easier and convenient for you to have fun with your kids at anytime of the day
Includes a 12V rechargeable battery and charger; Provides up to 90 minutes of run time which is enough for kids to maximize their adventure and fun all around

Style: 1200r Quad
Color: Gloss Black
This ATV ride-on is just right for ages 2-5 and a rider weight less than 65 lbs; begin the fun by just pushing the dashboard button to start the engine; goes 2.5 and 5 mph in forward and reverse for some serious fun
Cool features make every ride unforgettable; working LED headlights, roaring engine sounds, and horn sounds all create one exciting ride
Heavy duty components create a memorable riding experience; front and rear suspension provides an off-road feel while the two 6V drive motors let adventures extend beyond the sidewalk
Your little rider can listen to favorite songs while riding thanks to the MP3-compatible audio jack; just plug in an MP3 player and start jamming out
The charging port is conveniently located on the dashboard for easy access; two 6V rechargeable batteries (total 12 Volts) and handy wall charger included; delivers up to 40 minutes of continuous playtime on one charge
